                                    <h6>Try It Yourself</h6>
                                    <p>Call the endpoint directly, supply parameters, and download the response as JSON or CSV.</p>

                                    <div class="row g-3 mb-3">
                                        <div class="col-md-4">
                                            <label for="priceTypeSelect" class="form-label">Type</label>
                                            <select class="form-select" id="priceTypeSelect">
                                                <option value="NCPI" selected>NCPI</option>
